---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/Sections/PageHeader.astro";
import StaffList from "../components/Sections/StaffList.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Every Nation Tzaneen"
  description="Learn about our church's history, mission, values, and the people who make our community special."
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="About Us" 
    subtitle="We exist to honour God by establishing Christ-centred, Spirit-empowered, socially responsible churches and campus ministries in every nation."
  backgroundImage="/uploads/every_nation_churches_and_ministries_cover.webp"
  />
  
  <!-- Three pillars (Christ-centred / Spirit-empowered / Socially responsible) -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 text-center border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Christ Centred</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We remain centred on Christ — He is the foundation and cornerstone of everything we do. (Colossians 1:17-18)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 text-center border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Spirit Empowered</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We celebrate the presence and power of the Holy Spirit, who enables us to honour God and become effective witnesses of the Gospel. (Acts 1:8)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 text-center border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Socially Responsible</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We demonstrate the compassion and character of Christ to our communities and cultures, caring for people in practical ways. (Proverbs 14:31)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Core Values</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">The Apostle Paul exhorted Timothy to "guard the good deposit ... with the help of the Holy Spirit" (2 Timothy 1:14). These are the values that guide how we build and serve.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="/uploads/Lordship.png" alt="Lordship" class="w-14 h-14 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">LORDSHIP</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Jesus is "King of kings and Lord of lords." Whole‑hearted submission to God's will and His Word is the foundation of all spiritual growth. (Colossians 2:6)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="/uploads/evangelism.png" alt="Evangelism" class="w-14 h-14 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">EVANGELISM</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">God's heart is to reach the lost. We're passionate about preaching the gospel and doing ministry in a way that engages people outside of the Christian faith. (John 3:16, Luke 19:10)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="/uploads/Discipleship.png" alt="Discipleship" class="w-14 h-14 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">DISCIPLESHIP</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">We're called to make disciples by establishing biblical foundations and equipping believers to minister. (Matthew 28:19-20)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="/uploads/Leadership.png" alt="Leadership" class="w-14 h-14 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">LEADERSHIP</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">We develop leaders intentionally, creating platforms to raise the next generation of ministry leaders. (2 Timothy 2:2)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <img src="/uploads/Family.png" alt="Family" class="w-14 h-14 object-contain" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">FAMILY</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Family is the foundation of ministry. We embrace community, reject disposable relationships and walk in love and unity. (Psalm 127:1,3)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">SERVICE</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">We demonstrate Christ's compassion through practical service and community engagement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            To know Christ and to make Him known through worship, discipleship, fellowship, and service.
          </p>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
            To be a vibrant, growing community of believers who are transformed by the Gospel and transforming our community with the love of Christ.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493225457124-a3eb161ffa5f?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center" 
            alt="Worship at our church" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover w-full h-full"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Church History -->
        
  <!-- Church History -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our History</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The story of how our church has grown and evolved over the years
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative pl-8 sm:pl-16 py-6 group">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start mb-1 group-last:before:hidden before:absolute before:left-2 sm:before:left-7 before:h-full before:px-px before:bg-gray-300 before:self-start before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-3 after:absolute after:left-2 sm:after:left-7 after:w-4 after:h-4 after:bg-primary-600 after:border-4 after:border-white after:rounded-full after:-translate-x-1/2 after:translate-y-1.5">
            <time class="sm:w-28 text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase">1950</time>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Church Founded</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Our church was planted by Every Nation Tshwane, where God placed Pastor Willem and Family in Tzaneen to reach the community with the message of Jesus Christ.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Three-column leadership / family / statement layout -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">

        <!-- Column 1: Leadership -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Meet Our Leadership</h3>
          <StaffList showAll={false} limit={4} compact={true} />
          <div class="mt-4">
            <a href="/staff" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Meet All Our Staff</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Column 2: Family / Core Values -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Family</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold">LORDSHIP</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Jesus is "King of kings and Lord of lords." We believe whole-hearted submission to God's will and Word is the starting point of Christian faith. (Colossians 2:6)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold">EVANGELISM</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">God's heart is to reach the lost. We're passionate about preaching the gospel and ministering to people outside the church. (John 3:16)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold">DISCIPLESHIP</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">We build disciples by teaching Scripture and equipping believers to minister. (Matthew 28:19-20)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Column 3: Statement of Faith -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What We Believe</h3>
          <div class="prose text-gray-700">
            <p>In the Holy Scriptures as originally given by God, divinely inspired, infallible, entirely trustworthy, and the supreme authority in all matters of faith and conduct.</p>
            <p>In one God, eternally existent in three persons: Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.</p>
            <p>In our Lord Jesus Christ, God manifested in the flesh, his virgin birth, his sinless human life, his divine miracles, his vicarious and atoning death, his bodily resurrection, his ascension, his mediatorial work, and his personal return in power and glory.</p>
            <p>In the salvation of lost and sinful man through the shed blood of the Lord Jesus Christ by faith apart from works, and regeneration by the Holy Spirit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>